-- Russia to Draft Extra-Heavy Crude Tax Break by July 1, RIA Says
-- B y   S t e p a n   K r a v c h e n k o
-- 2012-05-06T06:30:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-06/russia-to-draft-extra-heavy-crude-tax-break-by-july-1-ria-says.html
Russia plans to complete proposals to
cut export taxes on extra-heavy crude by July 1, RIA Novosti
reported late yesterday, citing a government document.  To contact the reporter on this story:
